There is drama at the ongoing investigation into the Niger Delta Development Commission (NDDC) as the Acting Managing Director of the Niger Delta Development Commission (NDDC), Kemebradikumo Pondei slumped while taking questions from the members of the committee. The Acting MD appeared alongside the Minister for Niger Delta Affairs, Godswill Akpabio at the ongoing hearing by the committee. The session has been adjourned for 30 minutes.